    "video_length": "PT9M37S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "I am lucky to have the best friends in the world", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Friends fan of grand-prix first", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And fan of me aswell", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yeah give me a bike like this and I do better", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you do better I swear I buy you the bike", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I even buy you two of them", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yeah two of them", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to the point where they believe I can to handle a Moto2", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Did you find something ?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "yeah look we can rent a true Moto2 here", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A true race bike ?! No excuses he won\u2019t fool around", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We will soon be fixed on his skills", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And they did it !", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I am now in the holy and legendary Bugatti Circuit", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In company of some privileged and V.I.P people", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Aren\u2019t this the best friends in the world ?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I had to pull the wallet out too", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because at 1 500\u20ac the day, the dream has a cost", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But some say a dream has no price", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And as I had to take a loan", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I picked the whole package", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with the bike and a coach", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "J-M. Bayle or S. Charpentier if you please", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at 2 500\u20ac the day", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Needless to say that Fist On Track ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which offers this GP dream days", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "unrolled the red carpet for me", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I obviously did not spoke to the organizers", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ivan and Ludo", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about the time I had to do in order not to", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "lose the face in front of my generous friends", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There\u2019s just one thing I did not expect", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was out of question to ride in slicks under heavy rain", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There\u2019s some wet tires proposed of course", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and swiftly mounted by Vatea", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But the deposit check covering the cost of the bike", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "45 000\u20ac", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Led me to wait for the track to dry", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Meanwhile and to get started", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sebastien Charpentier himself ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "lent me his CBR 1000 with rain tires ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and even pampered me", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Did you say privileged ?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Come on man we must get back on track now !", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At First On Track there\u2019s several V.I.P courses", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Including a personal care by Bayle or Charpentier", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Who are taping you, debriefing you", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Giving you their little secrets", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The thing is to brake a little later", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to let the brakes go at the same point", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but as you braked a bit latter", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you will have like 2 additional km/h", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when releasing the brakes", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The V.I.P course, with the dream parking", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it\u2019s also a physio and real food", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What is this ? we have far better for you", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with real cutlery, real plates", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Energizing drinks like the true pilots", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "an engineer at your orders", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "tire warmers", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and even incredible hotels", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with swimming pool and guys playing the piano", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "other kind of pools", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sophisticated meals", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And even a completely devoted staff", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The tires are getting warm it will be good soon", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well unless it is a real dream this time", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Anyway I was there for good and", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by the time the track went dry", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I enjoyed looking every bits of the race beast", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with which I would finally reveal my skills", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in the eyes of the whole world", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It is a Suter from 2010", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "previously owned by the Racing Team Germany", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was the first year in Moto2", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The German pilot Arne Tode was in charge", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and achieved winning 2 points in the GBR race", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "won by a certain Jules Cluzel which had a Suter as well", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The Swiss manufacturer equipping 1/3 of the Moto2 bikes", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was present since the beginning and gave victory to", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a man named Marc Marquez ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "from which I took the helmet in all due respect", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The best way to achieve a fast lap", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When looking closer we see that it is a true prototype", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "With the large welds and single block pieces", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the electronic captors everywhere", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and adjustments at all levels", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The engine: a 4 cylinder Honda of 600cc", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has to be opened up every 1 000km to be inspected", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Combustible wise, we get stunned from", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the octane 110 fuel vapors that cost:", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "5,95\u20ac per liters  excluding taxes", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so for a 20 minutes session\u2026do the math", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not mentioning the Dunlop tires", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about 580\u20ac with a 195 width at the back", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but the specialists are better instructed than I am", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The first price is just the bike at 1 500\u20ac per day", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "en engine developing about 135hp for 135kg", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Some would like bikes more rigid\u2026some other less rigid", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I find the balance perfect and you can go really fast", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we see some mad races and that\u2019s no surprise", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then with Jean-Michel and Sebastien it\u2019s 2 500\u20ac", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with the supports during the whole day", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "\u00d6hlins shock fully adjustable", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "reversed \u00d6hlins fork fully adjustable", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because you are tensed on this kind of bike", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as they are truly race bikes, very rigid", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the more you are tensed the less it works", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then there\u2019s the V.I.P course for two days", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it\u2019s 2 400\u20ac including the hotel\u2026", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It\u2019s a 600CBR stock engine", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The bike is more precise", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You got it: the pressure is increasing", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that\u2019s for the best", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The man I pictured in my dream", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has finally arrived and will show me the way", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "With J-M Bayle,there is no chance that it will slip away", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I guess\u2026", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The multiple world champion in different categories", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "can show me the way", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "still the Suter cannot follow the CBR", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "With the MMX frame, precise and rigid", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Trajectories are not the same as with a 1000cc", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even if lap times can be similar", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When releasing the brakes at the end of a straight line", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the bike does not wiggles at all", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and gets exactly where you planned to", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Seeing how the Moto2 pilots", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are bending the frames and leaning on TV", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I am far from pushing to its limits this evil bike", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "however hauling to death at more than 15 000rpm", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The engine is not the most impressive on the machine", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even if the sound is literally mesmerizing", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After an improving session by Master Bayle ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I felt like risking it all at this Suter handlebar", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and therefore shut my friends mouths", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here I am in the Bugatti straight line", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I passed the six gears before throwing myself", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "into the fast curve and drop a gear", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "5th then 3 more before the Dunlop chicane", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "acceleration trying to avoid the kerbs", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "2nd then 3rd before the Chapelle curve", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I miss..no I got the apex and am trying to hold to it", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not exploiting it all... throttle back !", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The mus\u00e9e corner now, the chassis takes it ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "these bumps and I throttle again", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After the mus\u00e9e 4th then 5th gear", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I drop 2 no 3 gears before getting to the ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "double straight of the garage vert", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "three machines ahead I overtake the Kawasaki easily", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I\u2019ll try to get the others at the braking", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thanks the excellent brakes of the Suter ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I miss the trajectory", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "taking the apex though and throttling ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "exiting the chemin aux boeuf", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "4th, 3rd, 2nd before plunging in the blue S", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I\u2019m handling it not too bad...", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "apex...", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and then I get to the braking of the raccordement", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The chassis helps me getting in really hard ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In the raccordement...", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "...kerbs, apex again, accelerating...", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Alas my lap is at 10 seconds from", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the time I hoped for", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My friends are going to make fun of me", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I lived my dream", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for the time of a day I was a true GP pilot", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }
    ], 
    "title": "Devenir pilote d'un jour en Moto2", 
